collections.name: Find peace in the chaos with CBD
Aliens from the Portal
collections.description:
One night, a glowing hole appeared, pulsing with energy—a portal to another dimension. From it emerged The Cosmic Gatekeeper. I watched in awe and disbelief.
Since that night, I’ve taken it upon myself to document everything. I observe the portal, study it, and sketch each alien that emerges. These portraits are my way of understanding and sharing their existence with the world.  
If you choose to purchase one of these portraits, I must warn you—I cannot guarantee that the aliens won’t transfer to you through the illustrations. However, they are gentle and, honestly, quite cute. If you’re ready to meet them, the choice is yours.
